tspan.tspan: - lead_velocity_threshold: velocity of the lead vehicle
when there is no lead vehicle, in m/s (default: 50)
- backway_threshold: headway of back vehicle when
there is no back vehicle, in m (default: 1000)
- margin_list: set lower bound, step and upper bound
- T: safe time headway, in s (default: 1)
- s0: linear jam distance, in m (default: 2)
- alpha: gain on the desired velocity to the current
- beta: gain on lead car velocity and self-velocity
- wanted_max_accel: whether to reach the max
